parameters: \nc<>Oops, I accidentally killed them. What a waste.

\nc<>Everyone, it would be better if you stopped your futile
resistance and quietly let yourselves be captured.

\ncMagical Girl Lime, arriving as well. Hmph, I thought there
would be something more than just small fry.

\ncHey, don't we have to say some kind of introduction line!?
We're turning 20 this year, you know!?
\nc<Rose>If we do that, the citizens will feel relieved, right?
\nc<Rose>Everyone, please rest assured! We will help you!
\nc<Citizen>M-Magical girls! The magical girls have arrived!

\ncThank goodness, with this the tentacles are finally
finished...!

\nc<>Oh, I see. So there are three of them. I heard that the
neighboring town was busy too, but there are more than I
thought.

\ncI don't know what happened to the magical girls in this
town, but I'm going to catch you here!
\nc<>No, it's you guys who will be caught.
\nc<Lime>W-What, magic!? This small fry... how dare they...!

\ncSpear, spear!...I-I can't use magic! What on earth are
you...!

\nc<>Well, who knows? Maybe there's a spy among the magical
girls. Hehe.

\nc<>Now, go catch those kids. They're valuable samples, so
handle them carefully, okay?
